  <entry>
    <title>rollup环境搭建</title>
    <url>/2022/12/17/rollup%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>起因：在写小程序过程中，需要一些轮子，发现大部分功能都是基于Vue来做，于是心血来潮就有这个学习项目了</p>
<p>过程：学习Vue2源码，并学会一些代码思维，模仿即是学习</p>
<p>结果：正在学习~待以后回来填写</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h2><p>在项目目录下生成package.json</p>
<figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> init -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="rollup的安装流程"><a href="#rollup的安装流程" class="headerlink" title="rollup的安装流程"></a>rollup的安装流程</h2><p>安装：rollup</p>
<p>插件，编译高级语法：rollup-plugin-babel</p>
<p>核心模块：@babel&#x2F;core</p>
<p>预设，编译高级语法：@babel&#x2F;preset-env</p>
<p>开发依赖：–save–dev</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install <span class="keyword">rollup</span> <span class="keyword">rollup</span><span class="operator">-</span>plugin<span class="operator">-</span>babel <span class="variable">@babel</span><span class="operator">/</span>core <span class="variable">@babel</span><span class="operator">/</span>preset<span class="operator">-</span>env <span class="comment">--save--dev</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>两个编译高级语法的差别在于：配置文件不同，使用方式不同，都可以在Rollup 配置文件（rollup.config.js）使用，第二个也可以在.babelrc文件中使用</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="创建配置文件"><a href="#创建配置文件" class="headerlink" title="创建配置文件"></a>创建配置文件</h2><ol>
<li><p>创建配置文件：项目目录下，创建rollup.config.js</p>
</li>
<li><p>创建入口文件：项目目录下，创建 src &gt; index.js</p>
</li>
<li><p>指定打包入口和出口</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="regexp">//</span> 导入babel插件</span><br><span class="line">import babel from <span class="string">&#x27;rollup-plugin-babel&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export default &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="regexp">//</span> 入口</span><br><span class="line">  input: <span class="string">&#x27;./src/index.js&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="regexp">//</span> 出口</span><br><span class="line">  output: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="regexp">//</span> 出口文件</span><br><span class="line">    file: <span class="string">&#x27;./dist/vue.js&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="regexp">//</span> 全局变量名称</span><br><span class="line">    name: <span class="string">&#x27;Vue&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="regexp">//</span> 打包后的文件格式，umd: 用于浏览器、Node.js 和其他环境的通用模块定义</span><br><span class="line">    format: <span class="string">&#x27;umd&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="regexp">//</span> 希望可以调试源代码</span><br><span class="line">    sourcemap: true,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="regexp">//</span> 打包使用插件</span><br><span class="line">  plugins: [</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="regexp">//</span> 使用babel插件</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="regexp">//</span> 可以在这里加配置，但太长，所以在目录下创建</span><br><span class="line">    babel(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="regexp">//</span> 排除打包文件</span><br><span class="line">      exclude: <span class="string">&#x27;node_modules/**&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">  ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="创建-babel文件并配置"><a href="#创建-babel文件并配置" class="headerlink" title="创建.babel文件并配置"></a>创建.babel文件并配置</h2><p>在目录下创建.babelrc，打包时自动使用这些配置</p>
<figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="regexp">//</span> 添加预设</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="regexp">//</span> 预设可理解为：许多插件的集合</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;presets&quot;</span>:[</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;@babel/preset-env&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="添加执行脚本"><a href="#添加执行脚本" class="headerlink" title="添加执行脚本"></a>添加执行脚本</h2><p>在 package.js 中的 scripts 添加脚本</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;dev&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;rollup -cw&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>-c 指定打包配置文件 “rollup.config.js”</p>
<p>-w 监控文件变化</p>
<h2 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h2><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="built_in">run</span> dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="最后的目录结构"><a href="#最后的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="最后的目录结构"></a>最后的目录结构</h2><p><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/12/17/zbK3cT.png" alt="执行npm run dev之后的结构"></p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Vue2源码</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>开发环境</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>初始化数据</title>
    <url>/2022/12/17/%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>目标：创建实例对象并实现状态初始化</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<blockquote>
<p>响应式变化的核心：监听数据变化，包括取值和更改</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="实例化Vue"><a href="#实例化Vue" class="headerlink" title="实例化Vue"></a>实例化Vue</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dist/index.<span class="property">html</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> vm = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Vue</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title function_">data</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;Skiy&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">age</span>: <span class="number">18</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="建立初始化方法"><a href="#建立初始化方法" class="headerlink" title="建立初始化方法"></a>建立初始化方法</h2><p>为了保证代码可维护和低耦合</p>
<figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/index.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; initMixin &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./init&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/** </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 参数：options</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 功能：Vue实例化时传输过来的参数（实例化参数）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 类型：一个对象，可能包含 el、data、 methods 等等</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">function Vue(<span class="keyword">options</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">this</span>._init(<span class="keyword">options</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 这是一个引入使用即执行的函数</span></span><br><span class="line">initMixin(Vue);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export <span class="keyword">default</span> Vue;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/init.<span class="property">js</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 目的：给Vue增加init方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">initMixin</span>(<span class="params">Vue</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title class_">Vue</span>.<span class="property"><span class="keyword">prototype</span></span>.<span class="property">_init</span> = <span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">options</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="挂载实例化参数"><a href="#挂载实例化参数" class="headerlink" title="挂载实例化参数"></a>挂载实例化参数</h2><p>方便后续方法获取和用户调用</p>
<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/init.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">...&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Vue.prototype._init = <span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">(options)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/** </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    * this指向：Vue</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    * 原因：this._init这函数调用的</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> vm = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 实现挂载</span></span><br><span class="line">    vm.$options = options;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="初始化状态"><a href="#初始化状态" class="headerlink" title="初始化状态"></a>初始化状态</h2><p>状态：包括属性、方法、事件等等</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/init.<span class="property">js</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; initState &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./state&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">...&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title class_">Vue</span>.<span class="property"><span class="keyword">prototype</span></span>.<span class="property">_init</span> = <span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">options</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 初始化状态</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">initState</span>(vm);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/state.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/** </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 参数：vm</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 功能：初始化状态（data、props、methods等等）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export <span class="keyword">function</span> init<span class="constructor">State(<span class="params">vm</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 获取实例化参数</span></span><br><span class="line">  const opts = vm.$options;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 初始化 data 属性</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span>(opts.data)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    init<span class="constructor">Data(<span class="params">vm</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="初始化-data-属性"><a href="#初始化-data-属性" class="headerlink" title="初始化 data 属性"></a>初始化 data 属性</h2><figure class="highlight haskell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title">src</span>/state.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/** </span><br><span class="line">* 参数：vm</span><br><span class="line">* 功能：代理<span class="class"><span class="keyword">data</span>属性</span></span><br><span class="line">*/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title">function</span> initData(vm)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  // <span class="class"><span class="keyword">data</span> 有两种状态：函数或对象（一般用函数）</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">let</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">data</span> = vm.$options.<span class="keyword">data</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  typeof <span class="class"><span class="keyword">data</span> === &#x27;function&#x27; ? <span class="keyword">data</span>.call(<span class="title">vm</span>) : <span class="keyword">data</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>关于data为什么用函数：data的指针问题，若作为函数，那么到 initData 执行时指针才正真建立，而作为对象，从实例化时就确定了</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>会导致后面data对象劫持时是否显示在$options上的问题</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Vue2源码</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Javascript</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>响应式原理</title>
    <url>/2022/12/18/%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>目标：基于defineProperty，对 data 数据进行劫持，实现响应式</p>
<p>关键学习点：指针，闭包，递归，this指向（这应该包括在指针里吧）</p>
<p>技巧：…arg(作为参数) &#x3D;&gt; []，会转换成数组; newObj &#x3D; Object.create(obj)，obj作为“新创对象(newObj)”的原型</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="劫持-data"><a href="#劫持-data" class="headerlink" title="劫持 data"></a>劫持 data</h1><p>Vue2的问题：对整个data对象进行重写，性能差</p>
<p>Object.defineProperty 只能劫持已存在的属性（理解：新增的）</p>
<h2 id="劫持-data-对象"><a href="#劫持-data-对象" class="headerlink" title="劫持 data 对象"></a>劫持 data 对象</h2><figure class="highlight lasso"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/state.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; observe &#125; from <span class="string">&#x27;/observe/index&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">...</span></span><br><span class="line">function initData(vm)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">...</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 劫持 data 对象</span></span><br><span class="line">  observe(<span class="built_in">data</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在src下创建 observe -&gt; index.js</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/observe/index.<span class="property">js</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 判断data对象里的属性是否被劫持过</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Observer</span>(data)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title function_">constructor</span>(<span class="params">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="title function_">walk</span>(data);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 目的：循环data对象，对其数据依次劫持</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title function_">walk</span>(<span class="params">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title class_">Object</span>.<span class="title function_">keys</span>(data).<span class="title function_">forEach</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">key</span>=&gt;</span><span class="title function_">defineReactive</span>(data,key,data[key]));</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 参数target：整个data对象，key：对象的属性，value：属性的值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 目的：重写 data 对象的属性</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 特性：闭包，会保存上一次value的值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">defineReactive</span>(<span class="params">target,key,value</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title class_">Object</span>.<span class="title function_">defineProperty</span>(target, key, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">get</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> value;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">set</span>(<span class="params">newValue</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(newValue === value) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> value = newValue;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 参数：data 对象</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">* 目标：劫持</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">observe</span>(<span class="params">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 当为 data 对象时才劫持</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="keyword">typeof</span> data !== <span class="string">&#x27;object&#x27;</span> || data == <span class="literal">null</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Observer</span>(data);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<blockquote>
<p>关于劫持为什么只能是对象的原因：<br>若data里的属性作为一个值类型并处于第一层，那么它第一次创建实例就已经被劫持<br>而引用类型，只劫持当前的指针（也就是第一层），其对应的值（属性）并不会被劫持，所有才继续判断，需要结合后面才能理解这的写法<br>同时这里也为后面新增劫持作铺垫</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="让劫持的对象挂载-data"><a href="#让劫持的对象挂载-data" class="headerlink" title="让劫持的对象挂载_data"></a>让劫持的对象挂载_data</h2><p>劫持完data对象，此时若去打印vm（也就是实例），并不会发现数据被劫持，是因为data是一个函数（指针问题）</p>
<figure class="highlight lasso"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/state.js</span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">...</span></span><br><span class="line">function initData(vm)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">...</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 挂载到实例Vue的属性 _data 上</span></span><br><span class="line">  vm._data = <span class="built_in">data</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 劫持data对象属性</span></span><br><span class="line">  observe(<span class="built_in">data</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="代理-data的属性-到实例的全局"><a href="#代理-data的属性-到实例的全局" class="headerlink" title="代理 data的属性 到实例的全局"></a>代理 data的属性 到实例的全局</h2><p>目的：让 vm.name(原获取方式：vm._data.name) 能取到值</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/state.<span class="property">js</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">proxy</span>(<span class="params">vm,target,key</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title class_">Object</span>.<span class="title function_">defineProperty</span>(vm, key, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">get</span>(<span class="params"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> vm[target][key];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">set</span>(<span class="params">newValue</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> vm[target][key] = newValue;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">initData</span>(<span class="params">vm</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  ...</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 挂载到实例Vue的属性 _data 上</span></span><br><span class="line">  vm.<span class="property">_data</span> = data;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 劫持data对象属性</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="title function_">observe</span>(data);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 用 vm 代理 vm._data</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">let</span> key <span class="keyword">in</span> data)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">proxy</span>(vm,<span class="string">&#x27;_data&#x27;</span>,key);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>问题：若在get里面打印，其会输出两次，因为并非通过本身获取值和设置值，是通过已劫持对象_data来获取的</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="对象劫持"><a href="#对象劫持" class="headerlink" title="对象劫持"></a>对象劫持</h1><h2 id="劫持-data的属性-里的对象"><a href="#劫持-data的属性-里的对象" class="headerlink" title="劫持 data的属性 里的对象"></a>劫持 data的属性 里的对象</h2><p>可能看到主题会很懵，意思就是 <code>data:&#123; address: &#123; city:&#39;南极&#39; &#125; &#125;</code></p>
<p>实现方式：递归</p>
<figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/observe/index.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export <span class="keyword">function</span> define<span class="constructor">Reactive(<span class="params">target</span>,<span class="params">key</span>,<span class="params">value</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 在observe方法里有一个[是否为对象判断]若value为值类型就直接return了，该递归就停止了</span></span><br><span class="line">  observe(value);<span class="operator"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">  ...</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator"></span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>data的属性是对象时，劫持该对象后，挂载到全局的是该对象的指针，“设置”该指针的属性所对应的值是不会触发set函数的，但get会被触发</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="数组劫持"><a href="#数组劫持" class="headerlink" title="数组劫持"></a>数组劫持</h1><p>若不作数组劫持，它会把所有的数组的key都作劫持，这是不合理的，若有1000个值，会劫持1000次，浪费性能</p>
<p>而且数组大部分操作都是使用方法来增删改查，变异方法共有七个（修改原数组本身）</p>
<h2 id="劫持数组"><a href="#劫持数组" class="headerlink" title="劫持数组"></a>劫持数组</h2><figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/observe/index.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; newArrayProto &#125; form <span class="string">&#x27;observe/array.js&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Observer</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">constructor</span>(<span class="keyword">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 判断是否为数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(Array.isArray(<span class="keyword">data</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// 保留原数组特性，重写部分方法</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">data</span>.__proto__ = newArrayProto</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// 重写数组方法</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">this</span>.observeArray(<span class="keyword">data</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">this</span>.walk(<span class="keyword">data</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  ...</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  * 参数：data属性里的数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  * 功能：对数组里的值进行劫持，数组里的对象都会被劫持</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  */</span></span><br><span class="line">  observeArray(<span class="keyword">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">data</span>.forEach(item=&gt;observe(item)); </span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="重写变异方法"><a href="#重写变异方法" class="headerlink" title="重写变异方法"></a>重写变异方法</h2><p>创建 observe -&gt; array.js</p>
<p>目的：让数组函数的原型继承给newArrayProto对象的原型</p>
<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/src/observe/array.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 获取数组函数原型</span></span><br><span class="line">let oldArrayProto = Array.prototype;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// newArrayProto.__proto__ = oldArrayProto;</span></span><br><span class="line">export let newArrayProto = Object.create(oldArrayProto);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 所有变异方法: 指改变原数组</span></span><br><span class="line">let methods = [</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;push&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;pop&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;shift&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;unshift&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;reverse&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;sort&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;splice&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// concat、slice：不会改变原数组</span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">methods.forEach(method=&gt;&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 参数：args被转换成了数组: 1 =&gt; [1] </span></span><br><span class="line">  newArrayProto[method] = <span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">(<span class="rest_arg">...args</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// this指向调用该函数的对象：vm.hobby.pop(), 此时this就是hobby</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 调用原始方法：切片编程</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> result = oldArrayProto[method].call(<span class="keyword">this</span>,...args);</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 对新增的数据进行劫持</span></span><br><span class="line">    let inserted;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">switch</span>(method)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// push、unshift都是插入</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;push&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;unshift&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        inserted = args;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">// splice 增删都可以</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;splice&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 截取新增内容</span></span><br><span class="line">        inserted = args.slice(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="挂载-Oberver实例-到-data对象-自定义属性-ob-上"><a href="#挂载-Oberver实例-到-data对象-自定义属性-ob-上" class="headerlink" title="挂载 Oberver实例 到 data对象 自定义属性 ob 上"></a>挂载 Oberver实例 到 data对象 自定义属性 <strong>ob</strong> 上</h2><p>目的：是为了取到observeArray，同时为数据加了标识，证明被其已经被劫持过</p>
<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src/observe/index.js</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Observer</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">constructor</span>(<span class="keyword">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 此时的data可以是数组也可以是对象, 需要设置成不可枚举，不然会变成死递归</span></span><br><span class="line">    Object.defineProperty(<span class="keyword">data</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;__ob__&#x27;</span>,&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      value: <span class="keyword">this</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      enumerable: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/src/observe/array.js</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  newArrayProto[method] = <span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">(<span class="rest_arg">...args</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    let inserted;</span><br><span class="line">    let ob = <span class="keyword">this</span>.__ob__;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    if (inserted)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      ob.observeArray(inserted);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="识别是否已被劫持"><a href="#识别是否已被劫持" class="headerlink" title="识别是否已被劫持"></a>识别是否已被劫持</h2><figure class="highlight lasso"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export function observe(<span class="built_in">data</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">...</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 证明已经挂载到__ob__上</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">data</span>.__ob__ instanceof Observer)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">data</span>.__ob__;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="params">...</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
